    "λ: Regularization parameter, controlling the trade-off between fitting the data and regularization.",
    "N: Total number of network traffic instances.",
    "The problem formulation seeks to optimize the model's parameters, (Θ), to maximize detection accuracy while minimizing false positives and false negatives in identifying network intrusions.",
    "This study has the following research objectives:",
    "To evaluate and compare the performance of various machine and deep learning models, including convolutional neural networks (CNNs), recurrent neural networks (RNNs), and ensemble methods, for intrusion detection, and to develop optimization strategies that enable real-time detection of novel threats. 2."
